window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>She needed an escape. He needed her.</i></p> <p>Galina has been looking for a way out. So when she has the chance to get out of her kingdom and away from the man who wants to own her, she has no choice but to see it through.</p> <p>Even if it means collecting on a life debt from the worst decision she’s ever made.</p> <p>Davin’s mistakes are catching up to him. A lifetime as the royal screwup of the Lochlannian line has landed his people in danger. So when Galina shows up at his door in need of a betrothal, it might just solve all of his problems.<br> <br> Even if it means playing house with a woman who hates him.</p> <p>But their ruse is dangerous. Between spies, court politics, and an uprising that wants to destroy them both, they’ll have to decide if their lie is worth fighting for.</p> <p>If <i>they </i>are worth fighting for.</p>"; 
